file.name: expected_valid_enum_object.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Entities
  version: '1.0'
paths:
  /:
    get:
      operationId: getRoot
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ColorValue'
components:
  schemas:
    ColorValue:
      required:
        - color
        - value
      type: object
      properties:
        color:
          type: string
          enum:
            - blue
            - red
        value:
          type: integer
          format: int32
